9. The arrangement of claim 8 wherein; 
said pull-in head (15) includes a spring actuated retainer (14) which is designed and arranged to expand into a groove (26) of a female opening (9) of said hub (25), and 
said hub (25) includes an exteriorly mounted coupler releasing mechanism (27) on said hub (25) which is arranged and designed for squeezing said coupler (14) for disconnecting said pull-in head (15) from said coupler (14).
